Tel Aviv Medical Center
Israel
<mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

[ProMED-mail thanks Professor Berger for providing these data, which
further document the role of imported livestock in the spread of CCHF
in Iran, and the continuing hazard of nosocomial infection for
healthcare personnel.

A map of the provinces of Iran is available at
<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Provinces_of_Iran>.
and the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Iran can be accessed at
<http://healthmap.org/r/00Hj>. - Mod.CP]
